## 5. Shared Database Schema

### bookings table

| Field | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|
| id | UUID | Auto-generated |
| patient_name | string | From booking form |
| phone | string | From booking form |
| emergency_description | string | From booking form |
| payment_method | enum | cash / mobile_money / card |
| patient_lat | float | From GPS |
| patient_lng | float | From GPS |
| company_id | FK | Selected company |
| ambulance_id | FK | Assigned ambulance |
| driver_id | FK | Assigned driver |
| status | enum | pending / accepted / dispatched / arrived / completed / cancelled / denied / timed_out |
| payment_status | enum | unpaid / paid / confirmed |
| rating | int | Null until submitted |
| feedback | text | Null until submitted |
| created_at | timestamp | |
| updated_at | timestamp | |

### companies table
- id, name, phone, email, logo, created_at

### ambulances table
- id, company_id, ambulance_number, driver_id, gps_capable, status (available/busy/inactive)

### drivers table
- id, company_id, ambulance_id, full_name, driver_id (e.g. DRV-00123), phone, photo, status (available/on_trip/offline)

### users table (admins only)
- id, company_id, full_name, email, password_hash, role (super_admin/admin)

